<div class="row justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-md-8">

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body p-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.9;">Nesting is a vintage furniture and home decor store based in Winnipeg, Canada. Founded in 2014, we have been helping customers create beautiful, unique living spaces for over 10 years. We currently employ 12 full-time staff including sales associates, an interior design consultant, a buyer, a marketing coordinator, and warehouse and delivery staff.</p>
        <p style="line-height: 1.9;">Our store features a curated selection of vintage furniture including sofas, dining tables, beds, bookshelves, and storage units, complemented by home décor accessories such as rugs, lighting, mirrors, and cushions. We currently sell through our physical showroom in Winnipeg, and are now expanding online to reach customers across Canada.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body p-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Our Data Sources</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.9;">The product and category data in this application was gathered from the following sources:</p>
        <ul style="line-height: 2.2;">
          <li><strong>DummyJSON API</strong> — Product and category data fetched from <code>dummyjson.com</code> including furniture and home decoration items.</li>
          <li><strong>CSV File</strong> — A curated collection of 45 vintage furniture and home decor products created specifically for Nesting, including custom descriptions, pricing, and imagery.</li>
          <li><strong>Faker Gem</strong> — Simulated customer data including user accounts, shipping addresses, and order history to demonstrate the full e-commerce experience.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-4">
      <div class="card-body p-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Database Structure</h2>
        <p style="line-height: 1.9;">The application is built on seven interconnected database tables:</p>
        <ul style="line-height: 2.2;">
          <li><strong>Users</strong> — Customer account information</li>
          <li><strong>Addresses</strong> — Customer shipping addresses linked to provinces</li>
          <li><strong>Provinces</strong> — Canadian provinces and territories with tax rates</li>
          <li><strong>Categories</strong> — Product categories for browsing</li>
          <li><strong>Products</strong> — Furniture and home decor listings</li>
          <li><strong>Orders</strong> — Customer order records with tax information</li>
          <li><strong>Order Items</strong> — Individual products within each order</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>